schema.name: drawCircle
schema.description: Draw a circle with the given center and radius.

type.description: The type of shape to draw. Must be 'circle'.

x.description: The x coordinate of the circle's center.

y.description: The y coordinate of the circle's center.

center.description: The center point of the circle.

radius.description: The radius of the circle. Must be at least 0.
